/*
  
  All parameters such as attributes, ids and classes
  can either be placed on the same row as the tag or
  on a line below with a +1 indent.

  IDs are set using the # prefix like so:

  <tag>#<id>

  eg.
  content#main

*/

// -------------------------------------------------

section#main
  h1#big-headline

// -------------------------------------------------
// of course you may set ids using regular
// attributes (@)

canvas@id="painting"